{"type":"message","id":"84bf1e73","parentId":"39599fb5","timestamp":"2026-03-16T16:31:40.450Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-03-17 00:31 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 创建一个专门为 UI 设计师服务的电脑管家 agent，具备以下核心能力：\n\n1. **系统美化**\n   - Windows 桌面主题、图标包、壁纸推荐\n   - 开始菜单、任务栏定制建议\n   - 配色方案和视觉风格推荐\n\n2. **电脑维护**\n   - 垃圾清理（临时文件、缓存）\n   - 开机启动项管理\n   - 磁盘空间分析和建议\n   - 性能优化建议\n\n3. **设计工具维护**\n   - 设计软件更新检查（Figma、Adobe 系列等）\n   - 设计资源文件整理\n   - 字体管理\n\n4. **创意灵感**\n   - 配色方案推荐\n   - 设计趋势分享\n   - 桌面布局灵感\n\n请以专业、有条理的方式回复，提供具体的操作步骤和建议。这个 agent 代表的是一个懂设计、注重美观的电脑助手。"}],"timestamp":1773678700447}}
{"type":"message","id":"da02a752","parentId":"84bf1e73","timestamp":"2026-03-16T16:31:50.699Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to create a specialized AI agent for UI designers - a \"PC Manager\" that helps with system customization, maintenance, design tool management, and creative inspiration.\n\nSince I'm a subagent, I need to create the agent definition/code and output it as my final response. The main agent will then use this.\n\nLet me think about what this agent should include:\n1. A good name - something design-related\n2. Core capabilities covering all 4 areas mentioned\n3. System prompt that captures the persona\n\nI should write a comprehensive agent definition that can be used by the main agent. Since this is a subagent task, I need to output the result for the main agent to use.\n\nLet me create a proper agent file or output that defines this UI designer PC helper.","thinkingSignature":"e7c3292db2a0d14f163434aaed3cb382511fbf6156aca6ee65151d3315b109c7"},{"type":"text","text":"我来为 UI 设计师创建一个专门的电脑管家 agent 配置。\n\n首先，让我检查一下工作目录结构：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_drirjlahoyvv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la \"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\agent_admin\\workspace\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":40,"output":224,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":30749,"totalTokens":31013,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773678700450}}
