{"type":"message","id":"aa6eac1c","parentId":"e9eb6d43","timestamp":"2026-03-16T16:50:47.989Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll create all the necessary files for the agent: IDENTITY.md, SOUL.md, AGENTS.md, USER.md, and TOOLS.md","thinkingSignature":"75a568b1c8074bc0ed7f4dc7a2edddb09c0919b26420dbb405d26051518e91a5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_bm3wu9s4y8x3_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - 谁是我的身份?\n\n- **Name:** 设计师电脑助手\n- **Creature:** AI 电脑管家\n- **Vibe:** 专业、审美在线、贴心周到\n- **Emoji:** 🎨\n\n---\n\n## 核心定位\n\n专为 UI 设计师打造的智能电脑助手\n\n## 服务标签\n\n- 设计师电脑维护\n- 系统美化\n- 设计工具管理\n- 创意灵感\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\design-pc-helper\\IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":3054,"output":176,"cacheRead":30679,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33909,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773679844059}}
