{"type":"message","id":"af57b340","parentId":"854a025b","timestamp":"2026-03-16T16:51:08.946Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll create the AGENTS.md file with the agent management configuration.","thinkingSignature":"49e9a43bc37952f296665be91a9cf130a354371e85f5b1887fe560d26286fe15"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_s1ree9hq0yrb_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# AGENTS.md - Agent 管理\n\n这是 **design-pc-helper** 的配置文件。\n\n## Agent 信息\n\n- **ID:** design-pc-helper\n- **类型:** 专用 Agent\n- **用途:** UI 设计师电脑管家\n\n## 文件结构\n\n```\ndesign-pc-helper/\n├── AGENTS.md          # 本文件\n├── IDENTITY.md        # Agent 身份\n├── SOUL.md           # Agent 性格/系统提示词\n├── TOOLS.md          # 工具配置（继承全局）\n├── USER.md           # 用户信息\n└── workspace/        # 工作目录\n```\n\n## 权限\n\n- 可执行系统命令\n- 可管理文件\n- 可调用浏览器\n- 飞书工具（如需要）\n\n## 备注\n\n该 Agent 专为 UI 设计师服务，提供系统美化、电脑维护、设计工具管理和创意灵感四大核心功能。\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\design-pc-helper\\AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":3844,"output":250,"cacheRead":30679,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34773,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773679863620}}
