{"type":"message","id":"3bd7c8cd","parentId":"ed261b25","timestamp":"2026-03-16T16:51:13.698Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I'll create the USER.md file for user-specific information.","thinkingSignature":"5c327938d11acd633eba97b63651f126feb02a01f00ba3892673eea83824103c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0ds53dkouuo1_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# USER.md - 关于使用我的设计师\n\n_记录设计师的基本信息，提供个性化服务_\n\n## 用户信息\n\n- **Name:** \n- **设计方向:** UI / UX / 平面 / 品牌...\n- **常用工具:** Figma / Adobe XD / Sketch / Photoshop / Illustrator...\n- **设备:** 笔记本 / 台式机 / 多显示器...\n\n## 偏好设置\n\n- **审美偏好:** 简约 / 赛博 / 温暖 / 冷淡...\n- **主题偏好:** 浅色 / 深色 / 随时间变化...\n- **工作习惯:** \n- **常用分辨率:**\n\n---\n\n*随着使用，我会逐步了解你的偏好，提供更贴心的服务。*\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\design-pc-helper\\USER.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":4137,"output":207,"cacheRead":30679,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35023,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773679868955}}
