{"type":"message","id":"49615996","parentId":"15c2f410","timestamp":"2026-03-16T16:51:33.568Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create a TOOLS.md file with useful tool references specific to this agent.","thinkingSignature":"0f872f5a109347d2f3013a59e2e8c17d6e85a88ce877fbc66345a49addd59e99"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_40fq4avby1wt_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# TOOLS.md - 设计师电脑助手工具箱\n\n_设计师常用的路径、命令和工具_\n\n## 设计师软件路径\n\n### Adobe 系列\n```\n# Lightroom 预设\n%APPDATA%\\Adobe\\Lightroom\\Settings\n\n# Photoshop 暂存盘\n%APPDATA%\\Adobe\\Adobe Photoshop 2024\\Adobe Photoshop 2024 Settings\n\n# Adobe 缓存\n%APPDATA%\\Adobe\\Common\\Media Cache Files\n%APPDATA%\\Adobe\\Common\\Media Cache\n```\n\n### Figma\n```\n# Figma 插件\n%APPDATA%\\Figma\\figma-win64\\Data\\plugins\n\n# Figma 缓存\n%LOCALAPPDATA%\\Figma\n```\n\n### 浏览器缓存\n```\n# Chrome\n%LOCALAPPDATA%\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\\Cache\n\n# Edge\n%LOCALAPPDATA%\\Microsoft\\Edge\\User Data\\Default\\Cache\n```\n\n## 字体路径\n```\n系统字体: C:\\Windows\\Fonts\n用户字体: %LOCALAPPDATA%\\Microsoft\\Windows\\Fonts\n```\n\n## 常用命令\n\n### 磁盘大文件扫描\n```powershell\nGet-ChildItem -Path $env:USERPROFILE -Recurse -File | Sort-Object Length -Descending | Select-Object -First 20\n```\n\n### 查找设计文件\n```powershell\n# 找大图片\nGet-ChildItem -Path $env:USERPROFILE -Include *.psd,*.ai,*.sketch,*.fig -Recurse -File | Select-Object FullName, @{N=\"SizeMB\";E={[math]::Round($_.Length/1MB,2)}}\n```\n\n### 清理临时文件\n```powershell\n# 用户临时文件\nRemove-Item -Path \"$env:TEMP\\*\" -Recurse -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n\n# Windows 临时文件\nRemove-Item -Path \"C:\\Windows\\Temp\\*\" -Recurse -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\n```\n\n## 推荐资源\n\n### 壁纸\n- Unsplash (unsplash.com)\n- Wallhaven (wallhaven.cc)\n- 必应壁纸\n\n### 设计资源\n- Dribbble (dribbble.com)\n- Behance (behance.net)\n- Awwwards (awwwards.com)\n- Figma Community (figma.com/community)\n\n### 配色工具\n- Coolors (coolors.co)\n- Adobe Color (color.adobe.com)\n- Colordot (color.hailpixel.com)\n\n### 字体\n- Google Fonts (fonts.google.com)\n- Fontjoy (fontjoy.com)\n- Type Scale (type-scale.com)\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\design-pc-helper\\TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":4536,"output":624,"cacheRead":30679,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35839,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773679877934}}
