{"type":"message","id":"c34fd1ea","parentId":"323eefb6","timestamp":"2026-03-16T17:01:13.529Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在更新 TOOLS.md，使其更适合 Java 开发工程师。","thinkingSignature":"7687f36270c1abaebf21dc6d27965f3c5e127c9aaa9af91e6367bfc887aa3cbc"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2bzifshpg9b0_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# TOOLS.md - Java 开发工程师工具箱\n\n## Java 开发路径\n\n### JDK\n```\n# 默认安装目录\nC:\\Program Files\\Java\n\n# 环境变量\nJAVA_HOME\nJDK_HOME\n```\n\n### Maven\n```\n# 本地仓库\n%USERPROFILE%\\.m2\\repository\n\n# 配置目录\n%USERPROFILE%\\.m2\\settings.xml\n```\n\n### Gradle\n```\n# 本地仓库\n%USERPROFILE%\\.gradle\n\n# 工作目录\n%USERPROFILE%\\.gradle\\daemon\n```\n\n### IDE 配置\n```\n# IntelliJ IDEA\n%APPDATA%\\JetBrains\\IntelliJIdea2024.1\n\n# VS Code\n%APPDATA%\\Code\\User\\settings.json\n\n# Eclipse\n%USERPROFILE%\\.eclipse\n```\n\n## 常用命令\n\n### 磁盘大文件扫描\n```powershell\nGet-ChildItem -Path $env:USERPROFILE -Recurse -File | Sort-Object Length -Descending | Select-Object -First 20\n```\n\n### 找代码仓库\n```powershell\nGet-ChildItem -Path $env:USERPROFILE -Include .git -Recurse -Directory | Select-Object FullName\n```\n\n### Maven 清理\n```powershell\n# 清理本地仓库中的孤立依赖\nmvn dependency:purge-local-repository\n\n# 清理构建产物\nmvn clean\n```\n\n### Docker 清理\n```powershell\n# 清理悬空镜像\ndocker image prune -a\n\n# 清理构建缓存\ndocker builder prune\n```\n\n## 推荐工具\n\n### 终端\n- Windows Terminal + Oh My Posh\n- Fluent Terminal\n- Alacritty\n\n### 主题/配色\n- Dracula / One Dark / Nord\n- Powerlevel10k / Starship\n\n### 壁纸\n- Unsplash\n- Wallhaven\n- 极简黑白风格\n\n### 效率工具\n- Wox / Raycast（快速启动）\n- Listary（文件搜索）\n- Ditto（剪贴板增强）\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\design-pc-helper\\TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":6413,"output":492,"cacheRead":30679,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37584,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"to