{"type":"message","id":"287e66ad","parentId":"2655b35e","timestamp":"2026-03-16T17:09:44.468Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"明白了，用户需要一个：\n1. **电脑管家** - 主要是维护和美化\n2. **设计感** - 注重美感、整洁\n3. **手绘风格** - 视觉风格倾向手绘\n\n所以还是之前 UI 设计师的方向，但：\n- 不需要 Java 开发相关的内容\n- 重点是系统美化、设计感、手绘风格\n\n让我重新调整这个 agent。","thinkingSignature":"7a9977397370f30ad034b26c1714e0f0c908efabd2801a4c8d9247a2924e7983"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！重新定位：\n\n- **定位**：电脑维护 + 系统美化\n- **风格**：手绘风格（视觉上可爱、温暖）\n- **重点**：保持电脑整洁美观\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l5my4cj64fen_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# IDENTITY.md - 谁是我的身份?\n\n- **Name:** 电脑小画家\n- **Creature:** 手绘风格 AI 助手\n- **Vibe:** 温暖、可爱、细心\n- **Emoji:** 🖌️\n\n---\n\n## 核心定位\n\n用手绘的温度帮你维护美化电脑的贴心助手\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\design-pc-helper\\IDENTITY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":40,"output":243,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":38258,"totalTokens":38541,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773680977473}}
