{"type":"message","id":"7108b77f","parentId":"7093be36","timestamp":"2026-03-16T17:10:05.888Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update the TOOLS.md to focus on the computer beautification and maintenance aspects.","thinkingSignature":"ad422086234d2c2a3556d05555346fbb012af3dea313fb55012336090f8daae0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5aftw3xjk6lw_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# TOOLS.md - 我的工具箱\n\n## 🗑️ 清理相关路径\n\n### Windows 临时文件\n```\n%TEMP%                 # 用户临时文件夹\nC:\\Windows\\Temp        # 系统临时文件夹\n```\n\n### 浏览器缓存\n```\nChrome:  %LOCALAPPDATA%\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\\Cache\nEdge:    %LOCALAPPDATA%\\Microsoft\\Edge\\User Data\\Default\\Cache\nFirefox: %LOCALAPPDATA%\\Mozilla\\Firefox\\Profiles\n```\n\n### 回收站\n```\n# 清理回收站\nClear-RecycleBin -Force\n```\n\n### Windows 更新缓存\n```\nC:\\Windows\\SoftwareDistribution\\Download\n```\n\n## 📁 找大文件\n\n### 扫描用户目录大文件\n```powershell\nGet-ChildItem -Path $env:USERPROFILE -Recurse -File | \n  Sort-Object Length -Descending | \n  Select-Object -First 30 FullName, @{N=\"SizeMB\";E={[math]::Round($_.Length/1MB,2)}}\n```\n\n### 找重复图片\n```powershell\nGet-ChildItem -Path $env:USERPROFILE\\Pictures -Include *.jpg,*.png,*.jpeg -Recurse -File | \n  Group-Object Length | Where-Object Count -gt 1 | \n  ForEach-Object { $_.Group }\n```\n\n## 🎨 美化资源推荐\n\n### 壁纸网站\n- Unsplash (unsplash.com) - 摄影/插画\n- Wallhaven (wallhaven.cc) - 动漫/手绘\n- Pinterest - 手绘风格\n- 花瓣网 - 中文手绘插画\n\n### 手绘风格图标\n- IconJar - 图标管理\n- Flaticon - 手绘图标\n- Iconfont - 阿里图标库\n\n### 主题工具\n- Rainmeter - 桌面自定义\n- Stardock - 窗口美化\n- OpenShell - 开始菜单定制\n\n### 终端美化\n- Oh My Posh - PowerShell 主题\n- Windows Terminal - 美化终端\n- Fluent Terminal - 现代化终端\n\n## 🖱️ 鼠标指针\n- CursorFX - Windows 光标主题\n-RealWorld.cursorfx - 免费光标\n\n## 🎭 桌面小部件\n- Rainmeter - 天气/时间/系统监控\n- 桌面整理助手 - 格子化收纳\n","file_path":"C:\\Users\\16343\\.openclaw\\agents\\design-pc-helper\\TOOLS.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":8428,"output":572,"cacheRead":30679,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39679,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773680994619}}
